.el .ds Aq '
.TH omny 1  "omny 1.0.1" 
.SH NAME
omny \- TUI SSH dashboard & server manager
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBomny\fR [\fB\-c\fR|\fB\-\-config\fR] [\fB\-t\fR|\fB\-\-theme\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
TUI SSH dashboard & server manager
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-config\fR \fI<FILE>\fR
Path to a custom config file.

Defaults to ~/.config/omnyssh/config.toml (Linux/macOS) or %APPDATA%\\\\omnyssh\\\\config.toml (Windows).
.TP
\fB\-t\fR, \fB\-\-theme\fR \fI<THEME>\fR
Override the color theme (default | dracula | nord | gruvbox).

This overrides the theme setting from the config file.
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Enable verbose debug logging (written to stderr)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH VERSION
v1.0.1
